ta indecencia\nTanta indecencia\nTanta indecencia\nTanta indecencia."}],"tags":[{"tag":"resistance","category":"analysis"},{"tag":"bomba","category":"genre"},{"tag":"government","category":"analysis"},{"tag":"oppression","category":"analysis"},{"tag":"corruption","category":"analysis"},{"tag":"Delegación del Norte","category":"delegation"},{"tag":"Guillermo Mundo","category":"speaker"}],"uuid":"246f006c-ef40-4f45-b99f-065646b1aa23"},{"start_time":4020,"end_time":4080,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Hay ocho delegaciones correspondientes a diferentes regiones. Bomberas y bomberos han venido de todas partes para este momento histórico."}]}],"tags":[],"uuid":"8c89581b-96df-4b3d-9827-70384b569406"},{"start_time":4020,"end_time":4080,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"\"Se que rompe tambor\""}]}],"tags":[{"category":"_uncategorized_","tag":"Se me rompió mi tambor"},{"tag":"suffering","category":"analysis"},{"tag":"oppression","category":"analysis"},{"tag":"Blackness","category":"analysis"},{"tag":"racism","category":"analysis"}],"uuid":"4825af08-388b-47c7-a5fd-d6e865f5ee45"},{"start_time":4176,"end_time":3600,"annotation":[{"text":"\"El Azul de mi Caribe\"","bold":true},{"text":"\nEl azul de mi Caribe"},{"type":"line-break","children":[{"text":""}]},{"text":"El blanco de mi ilusión"},{"type":"line-break","children":[{"text":""}]},{"text":"El rojo de mi bandera tiene sangre de cimarrón"}],"tags":[{"tag":"bomba","category":"genre"},{"category":"_uncategorized_","tag":"Azul de mi Caribe"}],"uuid":"5a852d35-f167-494f-8b99-380010333ebe"},{"start_time":5760,"end_time":5820,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"\"Yo soy cimarrón\"","bold":true}]}],"tags":[{"tag":"Yo soy cimarrón","category":"song title"}],"uuid":"cbca598c-7ea5-435c-901c-cdc1b551ac89"},{"start_time":5760,"end_time":41880,"annotation":[{"text":"\"Yo soy cimarrón\" Delegación del Norte","bold":true},{"type":"line-break","children":[{"text":""}]},{"text":"